high_descs: Turn and face the counter to your left next to the stove.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the back counter.
Hold the lettuce over the counter near the salt.
Put the lettuce on the left side of the counter.
Pick up the knife to the left of the cup on the counter.
Slice the lettuce into rings with the knife.
Put the knife back on the counter.
Pick up one slice of lettuce from the counter.
Walk to the refrigerator on your left.
Open the refrigerator and place the lettuce on a shelf inside, close the door then open the door and remove the lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn right and walk past the stove then turn right again and walk to the trash can.
Put the lettuce slice into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Cut a head of lettuce, place a slice in the refrigerator, put the lettuce slice in the trash can.

high_descs: Go forward to the counter that is between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter.
Move back from the counter a little bit.
Put the lettuce on the counter between the fridge and the salt shaker.
Pick up the big knife that is on the left of the salt shaker and cup.
Use the knife to cut the lettuce into slices.
Put the knife down on the counter in between the lettuce and the cup.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn to the left and go to the fridge that is on the right.
Put the lettuce inside the fridge and close the door, open the fridge and remove the cold lettuce, close the fridge.
Turn to the right and go to the wall, then hang a right, go to the garbage can.
Put the lettuce in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in a garbage can.

high_descs: Look down at counter,  turn right, take a step up and turn left to be centered with the counter.
Pick up the cabbage on the upper right of the counter.
Take a step back with the cabbage and observe the counter.
Place the cabbage down near the left center of the counter.
Pick up the knife in the center of the counter.
Use the knife and cut the cabbage into slices.
Place the knife on the counter behind the salt shaker.
Pick up the second slice of cabbage from the right side.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the bottom drawer of the fridge and place the cabbage in and close the door.  Wait a few seconds and open the door to take the cabbage out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the wall, turn right again and head towards the trash can.
Place the slice of cabbage in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the cabbage in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right and then back towards the counter top.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is behind the drinking glass.
Look down towards the counter top.
Place the lettuce on the counter top beside the knife.
Pick up the knife to the left of the drinking glass.
Slice the lettuce with the knife.
Place the knife back on the counter top to the left of the drinking glass.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn to the left and then face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door place the lettuce slice inside, close the door. Open the refrigerator door and pick up the lettuce.
Turn right then cross the room, turn right once more to face the silver trash can.
Place the lettuce slice in the silver trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the slice of lettuce in the trash can.

high_descs: move to the right just a little bit, then face the counter again that you were originally facing
grab the lettuce off of the counter behind the glass cup
look down at the counter a bit more so
place the lettuce back down on the counter on the left side
grab the knife up off of the counter
slice up the lettuce on the counter
place the knife back down on the counter
pick up a lettuce slice off of the counter
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the right
place the lettuce slice inside of the fridge, let it cool then take it back out
turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn right again and walk to the end of the room again
place the lettuce slice inside of the garbage bin there
anns.task_desc: place a cooled lettuce slice inside of the garbage bin
